data.description: Budget-friendly residence with a recently revamped interior worthy of Pinterest that is light, bright, and rustic! Boasting two generously proportioned bedrooms and a full bathroom, the home offers a spacious living area with an open concept enhancing the room in the dining, kitchen, and living room areas. Two entrances provide convenience—one directly into the kitchen and the other featuring an arctic entryway. There is a fenced area in the back yard for your pawed family members. The shed provides plenty of storage space for your Alaska adventure gear. Nestled on just over an acre of land and in close proximity to Fort Wainwright and Eielson.
